    </edge>
    <data key="d0">Toyota Motor NA: Lake House Architecture for Data and Analytics</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kp51k6LY-2c</data>
    <data key="d2">Toyota implemented a Lake House architecture to converge on-prem data warehouses and data marts into the cloud. The goal is to address challenges with getting domain data from purpose-built on-prem systems into the cloud, improving time to market, and eliminating data duplication. The architecture supports various users including analysts, data scientists, and business users for self-service analytics.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
